Three backend fixes for the mobile parent flow:

1. childList() returned wrong keys ('class', 'section', 'admission_no')
   so DashboardScreen and ChildrenScreen showed children with name only.
   Now returns class_name, section_name, admission_number, roll_number,
   plus per-child attendance_pct for the current academic year.

2. Mobile parent BusTrackingScreen polled /api/bus/status every 15 s
   but no such route existed — it 404'd silently and the screen was
   stuck on "Bus not started" forever. Added MobileApiController::busStatus
   and /api/bus/status route (auth'd, outside /mobile prefix to match
   the existing screen's URL). Returns running/stopped/idle plus driver
   name, route name, and live coordinates derived from the active child's
   transport allocation.

3. Payment dates in /mobile/payments/history and /mobile/payments/{id}/receipt
   now include payment_date_display formatted per the school's System
   Config date_format setting. payment_date kept unchanged for backward
   compat with installed app builds.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.7 <noreply@anthropic.com>
